.TH mlkit-mllex 1 "@DATE@" "MLKit @PACKAGE_VERSION@" "lexer generator for Standard ML"
.SH NAME
.B mlkit-mllex 
- lexer generator for Standard ML.

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B mlkit-mllex 
file.lex

.SH DESCRIPTION
When invoked, 
.B mlkit-mllex
reads the file
.B file.lex
and outputs a lexer (written in Standard ML) in the file 
.B file.lex.sml

To learn more about using 
.B mlkit-mllex
, see the manual "A Lexical Analyzer Generator for Standard ML" available as 
.B @prefix@/share/doc/mlkit/mllex.pdf

.SH SEE ALSO
.B mlkit
(1),
.B mlkit-mlyacc
(1)
